               <p>Q. to Platt. Do you know the witness? is he one that brought the sheets?</p>
               <p>Platt. I cannot say, upon my word.</p>
               <p>Q. What are you?</p>
               <p>Platt. An old cloaths woman.</p>
               <p>Q. to the Evidence. Who sold the sheets?</p>
               <p>Platt. I two, and the prisoner two.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence.</p>
